Title: Add help text to "Archive events of hosts" command
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1613675183
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0b8

The command "Archive events of hosts" is bound to the rule "Check event state
in Event Console" to archive events of one host. To make this clearly visible
to the user, a help text was added to the command.
